dev.models.pet

Class Cat

  • java.lang.Object
    • dev.models.pet.Pet
      • dev.models.pet.Cat

  • public class Cat
extends Pet
    Project 0:

    The Cat class serves as a representation of a real-world dog found in the Shelter system. Cat instances hold information of its real-world counterpart as variables that are unique to dogs. This class serves one of Pet's child classes.
